{
  "stem": "2460.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Some Hungarian, I heard, but mainly Polish and Slovakian.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I heard the languages.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were also yelling, give us whether you have left.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because you won't need it anymore.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Things-- just crazy things.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But anyway, we walked to the-- towards a huge building.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And those were the showers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Also, very fast.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Take off all your clothes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Leave only the shoes and the belt, nothing else.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then we were walking through some concrete floors.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "A lot of-- it was wet all over and smelled the [INAUDIBLE] smelled from all over.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Very, very scary.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And my father hold me-- was holding my brother.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And my brother was holding me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we were walking.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And there were men standing with you know, the razor blades--",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--and the machines.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they cut the hairs.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And just one second, they cut my hair-- cut my hair, and quick into the showers.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But everything sounded so fast.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Everything, [GERMAN], this word.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we went into the showers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they-- I don't know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The-- the shower took about half a minute.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then we again, lines.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And there were some large shelves there with those prisoners.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they're throwing a shirt and a pants and a-- now, shoes we kept, I think.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Some of them, some of them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "If somebody had very beautiful, good boots or something, it was taken away right away and given this wooden boot.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was lucky.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't have nothing special.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And a little boy, so nobody needed it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I-- I-- I kept my shoes and the belt, like I said.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was given a pants and a shirt.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we were running into a big-- a huge room, probably a thousand people.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were sitting.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And those crazy-behaved people, very few Germans.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
